      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is original, with factory-perfect gaps and a finish that glows under any lighting. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing zero signs of bolster wear or aging, and still retains that distinct new-car aroma. All technological features, displays, and buttons function with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using genuine parts. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is as clean as the topside. Sold with a complete set of keys, original window sticker, and a comprehensive service dossier, this is a rare opportunity to own a flawless masterpiece that feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line.",
